nme.com/artists/AFI">AFI</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Architects">Architects</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/grandson">Grandson</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jean-dawson">Jean Dawson</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jpegmafia">JPEGMAFIA</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pvris">PVRIS</a> 。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Flinkin-park-tickets%2Fartist%2F703831" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处购买英国机票</a>， <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Flinkin-park-tickets%2Fartist%2F703831" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处购买国际机票</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3806065" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3806065" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3806065" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/linkin-park-jim-dyson-1.jpg" alt="林肯公园的艾米丽·阿姆斯特朗" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/linkin-park-jim-dyson-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/linkin-park-jim-dyson-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/linkin-park-jim-dyson-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/linkin-park-jim-dyson-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/linkin-park-jim-dyson-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/linkin-park-jim-dyson-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3806065" class="wp-caption-text">林肯公园的艾米丽·阿姆斯特朗。图片来源：吉姆·戴森/盖蒂</figcaption></figure><p>新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/linkin-park-from-zero-review-3811752">《From Zero》获得了<em>《NME》</em>的三星级评价</a>，评价这张专辑“将轰动的、震撼人心的体育场摇滚和一些令人费解的疲惫歌曲创作有趣地结合在一起”。</p><p> “至关重要的是，‘From Zero’必须被视为一种重置，其标题就是向乐队的前名 Xero 致敬的例证。因此，任何与他们的大师级唱片的不可避免的比较都必须牢记《From Zero》的诞生地：布拉德·德尔森、戴夫·法雷尔、乔·哈恩和筱田的有机愿望，再次以林肯公园的身份共同创作。”读。</p><p> “当 Linkin Park 加入时，全球摇滚乐界肯定会变得更加美好，而《From Zero》中的精英时刻——尽管有缺点——也证实了这一点。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-announce-from-zero-concert-film-for-2025-3814586">Linkin Park 宣布 2025 年“From Zero”演唱会影片</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
