70-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/lady-gaga-shawn-mendes@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/lady-gaga-shawn-mendes@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shawn-mendes">肖恩·门德斯</a>差一点就出演<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/wicked"><em>《魔法坏女巫》</em></a> ——了解更多信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/wicked-movie-ariana-grande-cynthia-erivo-3814095">《邪恶》评论：热门音乐剧将反重力的飞跃搬上大银幕</a></strong></li></ul><p>《<em>魔法坏女巫</em>》将于本周（11 月 22 日）上映，由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ariana-grande">爱莉安娜·格兰德 (Ariana Grande)</a>饰演格琳达 (Glinda)、<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/cynthia-erivo-interview-aretha-franklin-harriet-2574560">辛西娅·埃里沃 (Cynthia Erivo)</a>饰演艾尔法芭 (Elphaba) 和乔纳森·贝利 (Jonathan Bailey) 饰演菲耶罗 (Fiyero) 主演。然而，根据<a href="https://pagesix.com/2024/11/19/entertainment/lady-gaga-was-essentially-cast-as-elphaba-in-wicked/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>第六页的</em></a>报道，情况并非总是如此。 </p><figure id="attachment_3814049" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3814049" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3814049" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wicked_universalstudios_2000x1270.jpg" alt="阿丽亚娜·格兰德和辛西娅·埃里沃" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wicked_universalstudios_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wicked_universalstudios_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wicked_universalstudios_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wicked_universalstudios_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wicked_universalstudios_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wicked_universalstudios_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3814049" class="wp-caption-text">阿丽亚娜·格兰德和辛西娅·埃里沃在《魔法坏女巫》中。图片来源：环球影城</figcaption></figure><p>据匿名消息人士透露， <em>《魔法坏女巫》</em> ——现在由乔恩·M·朱执导——最初将由史蒂芬·达尔德里执导。在由于档期冲突而最终于 2020 年退出这部电影之前，达尔德里为其中的两个主要角色选择了完全不同的演员阵容。</p><p> Daldry 的版本会喜欢 Lady Gaga 饰演 Elphaba，Shawn Mendes 饰演 Fiyero。 《<em>第六页》</em>的消息来源称，达尔德里和 Gaga 曾多次会面讨论她的角色，并且在最终失败之前，她“基本上是在他的版本中扮演的”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3805387" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3805387" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3805387" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LadyGaga-new-single-video-teaser.jpg" alt="嘎嘎小姐" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LadyGaga-new-single-video-teaser.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LadyGaga-new-single-video-teaser-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LadyGaga-new-single-video-teaser-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LadyGaga-new-single-video-teaser-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LadyGaga-new-single-video-teaser-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LadyGaga-new-single-video-teaser-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3805387" class="wp-caption-text">嘎嘎小姐。图片来源：Samir Hussein/WireImage/Getty</figcaption></figure><p>自从达尔德里退出电影后，Gaga 将注意力转向了托德·菲利普斯不太受欢迎的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/joker-review-a-melancholic-psychodrama-punctuated-by-splashes-of-shocking-violence-2543865"><em>《小丑》</em></a>续集 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/joker-folie-a-deux-review-lady-gaga-3790522"><em>《小丑：双人舞》</em></a> 。虽然她的表演受到好评，但影片反响不佳，票房表现远低于预期。</p><p>她最近发行了即将发行的专辑中的第一首单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-lady-gaga-tackle-inner-demons-in-twisted-disease-video-3807760">《Disease》</a> ，并宣布将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/wednesday-adds-lady-gaga-to-season-two-cast-3812597">加入<em>周三</em>第二季的演员阵容</a>，就在几小时前，她还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coachella-2025-lady-gaga-green-day-post-malone-travis-scott-lead-line-up-3814558">宣布成为 2025 年 Coachella 音乐节的头条新闻之一</a>。</p><p>尼克·莱文 (Nick Levine) 在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/wicked-movie-ariana-grande-cynthia-erivo-3814095"><em>《魔法坏女巫》(Wicked)</em>的四星评论</a>中为<em>《NME》</em>写道：“到最后，你不会完全从座位上飘起来，但你肯定会着迷，在回家的路上欣赏原声带。有趣、丰富多彩，而且对局外人充满同理心，这部电影确实是《Shiz》。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-and-shawn-mendes-were-in-the-running-for-major-wicked-roles-3814579">Lady Gaga 和肖恩·门德斯角逐《邪恶女巫》主要角色的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
